            "notes": "This deck focuses on utilizing Slimefoot's ability to create Saproling tokens and dealing damage to opponents whenever a Saproling dies. The inclusion of cards like Goblin Bombardment allows for direct damage to be dealt using these tokens, while cards like Skullclamp provide card draw by sacrificing them. Squee serves as a resilient, recurring threat, ensuring a consistent presence on the battlefield. The deck also includes a variety of efficient removal and disruption spells to control the board and protect the commander. By combining these elements with ramp and mana fixing, the deck aims to overwhelm opponents with a swarm of tokens and aggressive plays while maintaining a strong defensive and disruptive game plan."
